<para>Calculates the <ref refid="structuw12_1_1three__el_1_1ri_1_1_a_b_s_projectors" kindref="compound">ABSProjectors</ref> for a given pair of ao and ri basis sets</para>
<para>Eigenvalues of the overlap matrix are assumed to be zero for values less than the maximum of <computeroutput>linear_dependency_threshold</computeroutput> and the maximum eigenvalue multiplied by <computeroutput>eigen_ld_threshold</computeroutput>. Default values for linear dependency taken from <ulink url="https://doi.org/10.1063/1.2712434">https://doi.org/10.1063/1.2712434</ulink></para>
